article_text:
A single car traffic crash in Wakulla County has killed a Crawfordville woman.

The Saturday morning crash happened on Lonnie Raker Lane north of Sweetwater Circle at Crawfordville.

Killed was Krista Shanell Smith, 29 years old.

The Florida Highway Patrol says Smith failed to negotiate a curve and lost control, striking head on with a tree.

Troopers say she died at the scene
